Summary

mmWave radar sensors enable around the clock, remote, contactless health care monitoring without the assistance of privacy invasive cameras or equipment. The accurate and reliable performance of an IWR radar-based monitoring system enables caretakers to scale their resources more effectively with the growing desire for at-home care.
